        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39465057/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39465057/" class="">第241页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Neferankhatun/" class=" " title="折蕉手牽手摧花">折蕉手牽手摧花</a>
                (行公義 好憐憫 存谦卑的心)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39465057">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“借助机构完成和保持的记忆⋯⋯”

⋯⋯由習俗塑造和保持⋯⋯</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-10-04 00:14</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “借助机构完成和保持的记忆⋯⋯”<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>⋯⋯由習俗塑造和保持⋯⋯
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







