        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35643101/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35643101/" class="">第23页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/husangdouban/" class=" " title="胡桑">胡桑</a>
                (但愿时间能触及一个身影。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35643101">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">记忆术属于学习的范畴，回忆文化则属于计划和希翼的范畴，后者有助于社会意义和时间界域的构建。回忆文化建立在对过去的各种指涉形式的基础之上，我们的论点便是：“过去”（Vergangenheit）完全是在我们对它进行指涉时才得以产生的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-07-18 19:26</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
